Global License Plate Capture (LPC) Cameras Market Insights
License Plate Capture (LPC) Cameras Market size was valued at USD 2.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 6.2 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 12.2% from 2024 to 2030.

License Plate Capture (LPC) Cameras Market Overview
The global License Plate Capture (LPC) Cameras Market is poised for significant growth, driven by the increasing adoption of automated vehicle tracking systems for security and law enforcement applications. In 2024, the market was valued at approximately $1.8 billion and is expected to reach $3.2 billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 9.2% during the forecast period. This growth is propelled by advancements in machine learning, AI-driven technologies, and expanding use cases across transportation, smart cities, and toll collection systems. The demand for high-resolution cameras and integration with cloud-based solutions will continue to boost market development.

